{"section": "3.21.4: Solving linear homogeneous recurrence relations.", "qid": 1, "instructions": "<div class=\"activity-instructions\">\n</div>\n", "question": "<div class=\"question\">\n <div class=\"setup flex-row\">\n  <div class=\"label\">\n   2)\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   Suppose that one of the initial values for the previous question is g\n   <sub>\n    0\n   </sub>\n   = 1. Which one of the linear equations holds for variables s and t?\n  </div>\n </div>\n <fieldset>\n  <div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember148\" style=\"\">\n   <input aria-label=\"s + t = 0.\" name=\"42\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember147&gt;\"/>\n   <label aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"\">\n    s + t = 0.\n   </label>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember150\" style=\"\">\n   <input aria-label=\"s + t =1.\" name=\"42\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember149&gt;\"/>\n   <label aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"\">\n    s + t =1.\n   </label>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember152\">\n   <input aria-label=\"3s - 2t = 1.\" name=\"42\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember151&gt;\"/>\n   <label aria-hidden=\"true\">\n    3s - 2t = 1.\n   </label>\n  </div>\n </fieldset>\n</div>\n", "choices": ["<div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember148\">\n <input aria-label=\"s + t = 0.\" name=\"42\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember147&gt;\"/>\n <label aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  s + t = 0.\n </label>\n</div>\n", "<div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember150\">\n <input aria-label=\"s + t =1.\" name=\"42\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember149&gt;\"/>\n <label aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  s + t =1.\n </label>\n</div>\n", "<div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember152\">\n <input aria-label=\"3s - 2t = 1.\" name=\"42\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember151&gt;\"/>\n <label aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  3s - 2t = 1.\n </label>\n</div>\n"], "answer": "s + t =1.", "explanation": "<div aria-atomic=\"true\" class=\"explanation has-explanation correct\" role=\"alert\">\n <p class=\"message\">\n  Correct\n </p>\n The solutions are s3\n <sup>\n  n\n </sup>\n + t(-2)\n <sup>\n  n\n </sup>\n . Plug in n = 0 and the result is equal to 1.\n <br/>\n <br/>\n s3\n <sup>\n  0\n </sup>\n + t(-2)\n <sup>\n  0\n </sup>\n = s + t = 1\n</div>\n"}